visual.name: CalendarVisualByMAQSoftware
visual.description: View key events directly on your Power BI reports with a calendar view.

dataRoles.description: Add URL column. Enable navigation on event's double click
dataRoles.name: EventURL

position.description: Select the position for the legend

labelColor.description: Select the label color for the legend

fontFamily.description: Select the font-family for data labels

fontSize.description: Text size is based on the length of the visual

fontFamily.description: Select the font-family for data labels

showAllEvents.description: Show all events in a day

fontSize.description: Month and Year title font size configuration

textSize.description: View size and navigation buttons configuration

buttons.description: Settings to show or hide 'week', 'day' and 'list' button

workHours.description: Settings to set work hours for 'week' and 'day' view.

startingWeekDay.description: Select week name to set start day of the week

currentTimeLine.description: Show current time line for 'day' and 'week' view

navLink.description: Click on 'dates' or 'week Number' to navigate to day or week

rtl.description: Display calendar orientation from right to left
